nodes.text: Hi Person1, I had an appointment today with Dr. Person2 at the Org4. I had blood work done and I like to leave a hard copy of the results with your office. Everything looks good except for my PSA which has gone from 2.93 in MM/DD/YYYY to 4.5 today (MM/DD/YYYY) according to the VA. I like Dr. Person3 thoughts and impressions prior to my upcoming (MM/DD/YYYY) visit. I drop off the report tomorrow morning if that OK.
